<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Masterclass: Acid-Adjustment Result</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/terminal.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="terminal-container">
        <header>
            <h1><a href="/modules/acid" style="color: var(--text-muted); text-decoration: none; font-size: 1.5rem;">&lt; Back</a> | The Formula</h1>
            <p>Your precise chemical adjustments for perfectly balanced citrus.</p>
        </header>

        <main>
            <div class="module-card" style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem;">
                
                <h3 style="text-align: center; font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Target: <%= target.name %></h3>
                <p style="text-align: center; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 2.5rem; font-style: italic;">
                    Adjusting <%= volume %>ml of <%= base.name %>
                </p>

                <hr style="border: 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">

                <h3 style="font-size: 1.3rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--accent-blue);">The Additions</h3>
                
                <ul style="list-style-type: none; padding: 0; margin: 0 0 2.5rem 0;">
                    <li style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.03); padding-bottom: 10px;">
                        <span style="font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1px;">Citric Acid Powder</span>
                        <strong style="color: var(--accent-blue); font-family: monospace; font-size: 1.1rem;"><%= citricGrams %>g</strong>
                    </li>
                    
                    <% if (malicGrams > 0) { %>
                        <li style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.03); padding-bottom: 10px;">
                            <span style="font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1px;">Malic Acid Powder</span>
                            <strong style="color: var(--accent-blue); font-family: monospace; font-size: 1.1rem;"><%= malicGrams %>g</strong>
                        </li>
                    <% } %>
                </ul>

                <h3 style="font-size: 1.3rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--accent-blue);">Execution Notes</h3>
                <p style="color: var(--text-main); font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.8;">
                    Using a precise gram scale, weigh the acid powders and whisk them directly into your <%= volume %>ml of <%= base.name %> until completely dissolved. Store chilled. Your liquid will now behave exactly like <%= target.name.toLowerCase() %> in any cocktail shaker.
                </p>

            </div>

            <div class="module-card" style="padding: 3rem; background: rgba(30, 45, 70, 0.3); border-color: var(--accent-blue); margin-top: 4rem;">
                <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; text-align: center; color: var(--text-main);">Signature Serve: Malic Pineapple Daiquiri</h2>
                <p style="text-align: center; color: var(--accent-blue); font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 2rem;">A classic Daiquiri profile with the lush, tropical notes of pineapple instead of lime.</p>
                
                <hr style="border: 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(138, 180, 248, 0.2); margin-bottom: 2rem;">

                <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2rem;">
                    <div>
                        <h3 style="font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--text-main); margin-bottom: 1rem;">The Acid Prep</h3>
                        <ul style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.8; padding-left: 1.2rem;">
                            <li>Use the calculator above to adjust fresh, cold-pressed Pineapple Juice to a <strong>Lime Profile (6.0% Total Acid)</strong>.</li>
                            <li>Whisk the calculated Citric and Malic acid powders directly into the juice until fully dissolved.</li>
                            <li>Bottle and keep chilled. Your pineapple juice now has the exact biting acidity and shelf-life of fresh lime juice.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 style="font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--text-main); margin-bottom: 1rem;">The Build</h3>
                        <ul style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.8; padding-left: 1.2rem;">
                            <li><strong>2.0 oz</strong> Light Rum (Spanish style preferred)</li>
                            <li><strong>1.0 oz</strong> Acid-Adjusted Pineapple Juice</li>
                            <li><strong>0.75 oz</strong> Simple Syrup (1:1)</li>
                            <li>Combine all ingredients in a shaker with large ice cubes.</li>
                            <li>Shake vigorously until frost forms on the tin.</li>
                            <li>Double strain into a chilled coupe glass. Garnish with a single pineapple frond.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </main>
    </div>
</body>
</html>